"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4041fd25c2465943702c0ac1d39f55861672e47e","tid":615579,"uid":23947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"警賊生時死時都一樣累街坊，紅磡果單交警瓜柴封路間接導致架大車夾死左個女人、今次又累死埋位鐵騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n紅磡發生致命車禍，一名警員被貨車撞倒死亡。警務處處長盧偉聰到醫院了解情況後表示，對於失去一名盡忠職守的同事感到很難過，他已慰問家屬。盧偉聰又說，今次是他一星期內，第二次來醫院，證明警員的工作崗位是充滿不確定性及危險性。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰又說，最近見到許多交通意外，呼籲駕駛人士要以負責任的態度駕駛，因為一個疏忽足以影響另一家庭。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母奴婢聰、briefing下你班同事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e900eb0a8b8592d5246d2d63a26d4b66e2a650","tid":615579,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bae4d40270872551f436c2c8962fd2e2c14bdc2c","tid":615579,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7774be2f391644c39785958d707da87c85649a87","tid":615579,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"唔係e單個鐵馬下嘛<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180212&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20303002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180212%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20303002&d=FpaXw7UbswzJMEzQO9lqQx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=5d84b32d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180212%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20303002&h=6f821cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180212&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20303002</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s